'''奇雲·馬克·菲臘斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Kevin Mark Phillips'''}}，{{bd|1973年|7月25日}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[东英格兰|東部]][[赫特福德郡|赫特福德郡]][[镇|小鎮]]希钦（Hitchin），是一名英格蘭前職業足球員，場上司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，退役後擔任教練工作。

菲臘斯擁有[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]戰後最高的入球紀錄，在232場比賽共射入128球，以30球成為[[1999年至2000年英格蘭超級聯賽|1999/2000年球季]][[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英格蘭超級聯賽]]神射手<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/euro2000/teams/england/squad/746261.stm |title=Kevin Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408103900/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/euro2000/teams/england/squad/746261.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，更獲得同年的[[歐洲金靴獎|歐洲金靴獎]]。菲臘斯亦曾效力[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]、[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]及[[阿士東維拉足球俱樂部|阿士東維拉]]。

菲臘斯出身修咸頓青訓系統但未獲簽約，因為身形欠佳不能當前鋒，在非聯賽球隊{{tsl|en|Baldock Town F.C.|波迪克鎮}}（Baldock Town）展開其職業足球事業時只能出任[[右閘|右閘]]。這名短髮球員最終憑敏銳的-{射}-門觸覺而成為出色的前鋒，在新特蘭時以伙拍「長人」[[尼埃尔·奎因|昆尼]]（Niall Quinn）而著名，但菲臘斯在不同的球隊與不同類型的前鋒搭配亦有不錯的效果。

==球會==
===早年===
菲臘斯在[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]青年軍接受訓練，曾訓練出[[阿兰·希勒|舒利亞]]及[[馬菲·拿鐵斯|拿鐵斯]]等著名前鋒的青年軍教練{{tsl|en|David Merrington|戴夫·梅林顿}}（Dave Merrington）認定身材矮小的菲臘斯不適合當前鋒，經常安排他踢右閘位置，最後提議當時的領隊{{tsl|en|Chris Nicholl|克里斯·尼科尔}}（Chris Nicholl）放棄菲臘斯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3128127.stm |title=Saints find faith in Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005444/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3128127.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

菲臘斯被棄用後，隨即被當地半職業球隊波迪克鎮（Baldock Town）選中，司職右閘，但他的控球技巧及進攻意識迅即獲得注意，球隊將菲臘斯調任前鋒。菲臘斯的入球將波廸克鎮帶到聯賽榜的前列位置，而在如[[英格蘭足總錦標|足總錦標]]等盃賽亦獲得不俗的成績。菲臘斯優異的演出使他獲得機會加盟[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]球隊[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]。

===屈福特===
1994/95年度菲臘斯獲得屈福特的領隊[[格伦·罗德尔|-{zh-hans:格伦·罗德尔;zh-hk:格連·路達;zh-tw:格倫·羅德爾;}-]]賞識，於1994年12月19日以1萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]收購菲臘斯，由於陣內傷兵滿營，菲臘斯獲機上陣，並以其入球能力而獲認同。

翌季（1995/96年）屈福特雖然在榜末掙扎，但菲臘斯表現出色，不幸季末因腳傷而休戰長達1年。當他復出時屈福特已降級到乙組〈第三級〉，位處中游。菲臘斯原本與{{tsl|en|George Burley|乔治·伯利}}（George Burley）洽妥私人條件，準備加盟[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]，但因高達25萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的轉會費而拉倒。稍後菲臘斯在短時間內射入4球，包括對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]的[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，但直到球季完結，菲臘斯再沒有取得入球。季後以更高的60萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉會費加盟[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]。

===新特蘭===
菲臘斯在1997年夏季與[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]的轉會交易接近完成，但葉士域治拒絕支付額外的5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]而取消交易。[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]隨即介入，先付35萬英鎊以獲得菲臘斯投效，加出場次數及球隊成績等附加條款令最終轉會費可超越60萬英鎊。菲臘斯在新特蘭與[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]長人[[尼埃爾·奎因|昆尼]]（Niall Quinn）組成一高一矮而有極高效率的攻擊拍檔，菲臘斯停不了的入球使他成為新特蘭日後升級[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|超級聯賽]]獲得好成績的風雲人物。他的表現更贏得「超級奇夫」（''Super Kev''）的綽號。

新球季首場比賽因菲臘斯在上季季尾在舊球隊屈福特領[[紅牌|紅牌]]而跨季停賽，初期球隊需掙扎以獲取好成績，新加盟的菲臘斯亦因輕微的傷患而影響表現，但由1997年12月13日對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]到1998年1月17日對[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]連續7場比賽有入球，包括[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第三圈對[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]的「四喜臨門」。4月25日主場3-0擊敗[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]，菲臘斯成為新特蘭自[[布莱恩·克拉夫|-{zh-hans:布莱恩·克拉夫;zh-hk:白賴仁·哥洛夫;zh-tw:布萊恩·克拉夫;}-]]（Brian Clough）後首名一季射入超過30球的球員。新特蘭在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|甲組聯賽《第二級》]]僅以1分之微不敵[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]而失去自動升級席位，季後升級附加賽準決賽對[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，菲臘斯在次回合主場射入一球，協助球隊兩回合累計3-2晉級決賽。5月25日[[溫布萊球場|-{zh-hk:溫布萊;zh-hans:温布利}-]]附加賽決賽對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]，菲臘斯在下半場58分鐘射入協助新特蘭反超前2-1，但在稍後因傷退下火線，雙方加時後踢成4-4平手，十二碼查爾頓險勝7-6，新特蘭錯失升級機會，菲臘斯其後形容該場決賽為「在足球最失望的一日」<ref>[http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/football_league/article1848352.ece Phillips is hoping not to pay the promotion penalty]</ref>。總計菲臘斯在新特蘭首季共射入35球。

1998/99年開季菲臘斯狀態大勇，到9月中已射入8球，協助新特蘭爬升到聯賽榜首位，但1998年9月15日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]對[[切斯特城足球俱乐部|切斯特城]]，菲臘斯雖然射入一球協助新特蘭3-0獲勝，但下半場初弄傷腳趾導致需休戰接近4個月。菲臘斯的缺陣對爭取升級的新特蘭是個嚴重的打擊，但隊友齊心協力，在下場聯賽7-0狂數[[牛津联足球俱乐部|牛津联]]。菲臘斯直到1999年1月9日才復出作客[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]，一記遠射打開紀錄，最終2-2平手。菲臘斯仍需時間恢復傷前的狀態，在4場比賽交白卷後重拾射門鞋。到4月新特蘭已確保升級資格，4月13日作客[[伯利足球俱乐部|伯利]]以5-2大勝，菲臘斯再度「四喜臨門」。菲臘斯的入球能力使他首次獲召加入[[英格蘭足球代表隊|國家隊]]，作客出戰[[匈牙利國家足球隊|匈牙利]]。球季結束，新特蘭以105分奪得聯賽冠軍，順利升上超級聯賽，菲臘斯在26場聯賽射入23球，全部比賽合計射入25球。

新特蘭雖然以破紀錄的高分升級，但[[1999年至2000年英格蘭超級聯賽|季前]]大部分預測仍然抱懷疑的態度，預計新特蘭將在頂級聯賽中掙扎求存。新特蘭在[[英格兰东北|東北部]]死敵[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]的球迷更在他們的球迷雜誌「The Mag」列舉多項理由預測新特蘭將在季後降級，其中部分採納名宿及球評家{{tsl|en|Rodney Marsh (footballer)|罗德尼·玛什}}（Rodney Marsh）的論點，認定菲臘斯「千辛萬苦也入不到6球」。這些言論激發菲臘斯的鬥志，回應馬殊的評論，菲臘斯在9月中已射入6球，1月中20球，季尾更達到30球，對一名數年前尚在非聯賽球隊效力的前鋒來說，是一個豐盛回報的球季。1999年8月10日菲臘斯在主場2-0擊敗舊球會屈福特包辦兩球，展開其超級聯賽入球序幕。8月25日「東北打吡」作客紐卡素，下半場射入一球協助新特蘭2-1反勝紐卡素。9月18日在大勝[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]5-0一役連中三元。菲臘斯其中一個金球是在12月4日主場4-1擊敗[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]離門30[[碼|碼]]的一個「半窩利」（half-volley）入球。2000年2月5日主場再戰紐卡素，新特蘭先落後兩球，菲臘斯連追兩球，雙方各二平手，在「東北打吡」新特蘭一勝一和稍佔先機，菲臘斯兩場射入3球。球季結束，新特蘭排於聯賽榜第7位，壓倒同是來自東北部的紐卡素（第11位）及米杜士堡（第12位）。菲臘斯的第30個入球在5月6日聯賽最後一場主場對[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]時取得，入球全部在聯賽中射入，使他成為[[1999年至2000年英格蘭超級聯賽|1999/2000年]][[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|超級聯賽]]神射手及[[歐洲金靴獎|歐洲金靴獎]]的得主，直到2008/09赛季结束為止，菲臘斯仍是唯一一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]球員獲得歐洲金靴獎的榮譽。

[[2000年至2001年英格蘭超級聯賽|2000/01年球季]]是菲臘斯鞏固其射手地位的一季，在聯賽中交出14個入球，協助新特蘭連續兩年在超級聯賽獲得第7位。菲臘斯在場中除入球外，需要兼顧傳球及助攻，第二季開始被對方防守球員視為頭號監察目標，入球變得更困難。菲臘斯在2000年[[节礼日|拆禮物日]]作客對[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|巴拉福特]]大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]後狀態大跌，加上昆尼經常因傷缺陣，有兩個月完全沒有入球，直到2001年5月5日對查爾頓才以一球「窩利」（volley）打破悶局，再在5月19日聯賽最後一場作客2-2賽和[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]包辦兩個入球。總計全季在各項比賽共射入18球。

菲臘斯在渡過兩個令人失望的球季後才離開新特蘭。[[2001年至2002年英格蘭超級聯賽|2001/02年球季]]開季菲臘斯尚可保持狀態，2002年[[元旦|元旦]]對阿士東維拉射失其連續第三個十二碼後，菲臘斯決定放棄擔任「劊子手」<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/1737773.stm Phillips quits as penalty taker]</ref>。季尾最後一場菲臘斯在主場射入一球，1-1賽和[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]，而葉士域治在同時舉行的比賽以0-5大敗給[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]，新特蘭才排在榜末安全線上的第17位，倖免降級。總結菲臘斯整季共射入13球，因不滿現狀，曾在季中傳聞要求轉會。

由於上季成績差劣，領隊[[彼得·列特|彼得·里德]]（Peter Reid）承諾在夏天增強實力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2162442.stm |title=Reid desperate to spend |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031223133313/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2162442.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但沒有實現<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2173437.stm |title=Clouds loom over Sunderland |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031223123114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2173437.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而剛動手術復出的菲臘斯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2157733.stm |title=Phillips' pre-season boost |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530003411/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2157733.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>更於季前熱身賽對[[皇家安特卫普足球俱乐部|皇家安特卫普]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2165949.stm |title=New injury blow for Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307094815/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2165949.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[西維爾足球會|西維爾]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2182563.stm |title=New Phillips injury blow |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530002443/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2182563.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>時連番受傷。直到8月30日轉會限期關閉前列特才怱怱從[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]收購[[托雷·安德烈·費奧|費奧]]，代替轉任球員兼教練的昆尼的位置<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2225278.stm |title=Flo joins Sunderland |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2002-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021231005905/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2225278.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時在葉士域治購入{{tsl|en|Marcus Stewart|马库斯·斯图尔特}}（Marcus Stewart），兩人身價合共1,000萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2225953.stm |title=Sunderland grab Stewart |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530004904/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2225953.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，對新特蘭的財政做成沉重的壓力。8月31日憑處子登場的費奧的入球主場1-1逼和[[曼聯|曼聯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2224543.stm |title=Sunderland hold Man Utd |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040415233356/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2224543.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>後，菲臘斯需要接受[[疝氣|疝氣]]手術而休戰6周<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2248889.stm |title=Phillips out for six weeks |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031221213138/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2248889.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在菲臘斯缺陣時，新特蘭經歷五連敗<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2307715.stm |title=Five costly defeats |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040523125416/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2307715.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，領隊彼得·列特在10月7日被撤職<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2307679.stm |title=Sunderland sack Reid |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040429111133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2307679.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由[[侯活·韋健遜|侯活·韋健遜]]（Howard Wilkinson）接任<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2315749.stm |title=Wilkinson takes Sunderland job |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040518075245/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2315749.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。韋健遜質疑新特蘭球員的體力，惟獨對菲臘斯稱讚有加<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2395265.stm |title=Wilkinson doubts Black Cats' fitness |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040420203110/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2395265.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。昆尼終於在11月10日因長期背傷宣佈掛靴<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2438489.stm |title=Farewell to the mighty Quinn |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2002-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021112030449/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2438489.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，結束與菲臘斯的成功組合。12月9日新特蘭主場0-3負於[[曼城|曼城]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2535787.stm |title=City sink sad Sunderland |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040605144156/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2535787.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，下半場菲臘斯被換離場時拍掌及向在場球迷揮手，狀似說再見<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2560813.stm |title=Phillips' farewell hint |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2002-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021221073154/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2560813.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再次帶來轉會的猜測<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/sports_talk/2561929.stm |title=Should Phillips seek pastures new? |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2002-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021228131754/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/sports_talk/2561929.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後向韋健遜解釋說是感到失望的發洩<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2565487.stm |title=Wilkinson denies Phillips rift |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2002-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021221164159/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2565487.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月21日對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]菲臘斯包辦兩個入球將比數追平2-2<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2575485.stm |title=Phillips pegs back Baggies |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2004-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040710165553/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2575485.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後韋健遜誓言會說服菲臘斯留隊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2599131.stm |title=Wilko vows to keep Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530004345/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2599131.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2003年3月10日在執教20場僅獲兩勝後，領隊韋健遜被解職<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/2838339.stm |title=Fans' shock at Wilkinson departure |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2017-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804052700/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/2838339.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[米克·麥卡錫|米克·麥卡錫]]走馬上任<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2838747.stm |title=McCarthy unveiled as Sunderland boss |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116114711/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2838747.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月11日菲臘斯透露將會在季後被負債高達3,000萬英鎊的新特蘭賣走<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2938617.stm |title=Phillips hints at exit |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005858/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/2938617.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而麥卡菲更想儘早出售隊中有價值的球員為下季重建陣容作準備<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3011529.stm |title=McCarthy to ring changes |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005954/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3011529.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月11日最後一場聯賽主場0-4大敗給[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2978129.stm |title=Ljungberg treble sinks Sunderland |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2978129.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>後，新特蘭只獲得4膀7和破紀錄的19分，全季只有21個入球，位列聯賽榜末，來季降級甲組〈第二級〉聯賽。菲臘斯全季只有9個入球，其中6球為聯賽入球，首次未達雙位數的入球。

季後新特蘭進行大清洗，有傳米杜士堡有意收購菲臘斯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/middlesbrough/2985040.stm |title=Boro confirm Phillips interest |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030810122815/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/middlesbrough/2985040.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直到7月4日仍沒有球會出價達到新特蘭要求的400萬英鎊，麥卡菲警告不會在轉會限期前大平賣<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3044928.stm |title=McCarthy warns bargain hunters |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005446/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3044928.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月13日新特蘭主席鮑伯·墨瑞（Bob Murray）致電職業球員工會（Professional Footballers' Association）要求延期支薪給球員，凸顯新特蘭的財務問題嚴峻<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3062799.stm |title=Sunderland play down financial fears |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030930222825/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3062799.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然菲臘斯已獲發新球季的19號球衣，但麥卡菲預計菲臘斯即將離隊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3090767.stm |title=McCarthy set to lose Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030801082307/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3090767.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終於8月6日修咸頓先出價300萬英鎊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3126319.stm |title=Saints agree £3m Phillips fee |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archive-date=2003-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031102052842/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/3126319.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成功在8月14日以325萬英鎊將菲臘斯帶回其當初接受青訓的修咸頓。

菲臘斯不單因大量入球而獲得新特蘭支持者的崇敬，而是其全面的足球技巧，雖然身材矮小，但左右腳運用純熟，頭球了得，長程遠射更力發千鈞，在超級聯賽首季便轟入屈福特、車路士、[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]及[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]的大門。同時菲臘斯並不自私，與昆尼組成國內最令人生畏的攻擊組合，兩人首三季合共攻入143個入球可見一斑。菲臘斯為新特蘭在聯賽上陣209場，射入115球，平均兩場射入超過一球。

===修咸頓===
新特蘭在2003年降級後，菲臘斯離開[[英格兰东北|東北部]]的「黑貓」，以325萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]南下加盟青年時期受訓的修咸頓<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3150981.stm |title=Southampton land Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2004-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040716135259/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3150981.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，伙拍高大強悍的[[占士·比亞堤|比亞堤]]在前線攻堅。8月16日首次披甲即射入一球，協助修咸頓作客2-2迫和[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3140897.stm |title=Saints ruin Foxes' return |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2003-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030815200216/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3140897.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，獲得領隊[[戈登·斯特拉坎|史特根]]的讚賞<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3157167.stm |title=Phillips delights Strachan |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530003120/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3157167.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而球迷更希望菲臘斯能繼承退役的[[馬菲·拿鐵斯|拿鐵斯]]的7號球衣<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3158111.stm |title=Phillips in seventh heaven |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005503/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3158111.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。到9月尾，菲臘斯及比亞堤合共射入8球，而修咸頓亦進佔聯賽榜第四位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3125908.stm |title=Strachan praises strike force |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2003-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031014064947/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3125908.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。重返歐洲戰場的修咸頓於9月24日在[[欧洲联盟杯|欧洲联盟杯]]第一圈首回合主場迎戰[[布加勒斯特星隊|布加勒斯特星隊]]，菲臘斯射入扳平1-1<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/3131768.stm |title=Saints held by Steaua |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2009-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090810200424/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/3131768.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但其後作客僅負0-1，累計1-2被淘汰<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/3190032.stm |title=Steaua stun Saints |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040713045813/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/3190032.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月27日主場0-1負於[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]，除結束修咸頓季初不敗走勢外，菲臘斯更於完場前被罰[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3122916.stm |title=Boro stun Saints |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2003-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031009124327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3122916.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，停賽3場<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3189926.stm |title=FA clears Queudrue |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2003-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031216212708/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3189926.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月29日主場對[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]僅負0-1<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3349131.stm |title=Southampton 0-1 Arsenal |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530002144/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3349131.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在比賽中菲臘斯曾踏到對方門將[[延斯·莱曼|列文]]，在球證鳴笛完場後，列文用皮球擲中菲臘斯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/arsenal/3358815.stm |title=Lehmann stands firm |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040102055510/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/arsenal/3358815.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後菲臘斯為此被[[英格蘭足球總會|足總]]罰款1,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3523519.stm |title=Phillips fined by FA |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005246/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3523519.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

直到2004年1月7日再對[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]時菲臘斯已連續16場沒有取得入球，而修咸頓亦三連敗，雙方0-0言和<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3362529.stm |title=Southampton 0-0 Leicester |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040719170101/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3362529.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後被球迷大喝倒采，史特根為菲臘斯作出辯護<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3378427.stm |title=Strachan defends Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005633/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3378427.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月17日主場2-1擊敗[[利兹联足球俱乐部|列斯聯]]菲臘斯才告打破入球荒<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3385511.stm |title=Southampton 2-1 Leeds |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040117150907/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3385511.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1月31日梅開二度仍不能阻止修咸頓以2-3負於[[曼聯|曼聯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3417887.stm |title=Man Utd 3-2 Southampton |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2014-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724042647/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3417887.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。領隊史特根在3月離任，{{tsl|en|Paul Sturrock|保羅·斯特羅克}}（Paul Sturrock）接手上場，3月27日主場1-0擊敗[[托特纳姆足球俱乐部|熱刺]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3553015.stm |title=Southampton 1-0 Tottenham |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530010203/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3553015.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，菲臘斯不滿被換離場而與斯特羅克發生爭執<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3552975.stm |title=Sturrock shrugs off bust-up |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040421061228/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3552975.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月3日對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]時再次梅開二度，4-1作客輕勝<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3571945.stm |title=Wolves 1-4 Southampton |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040411101130/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3571945.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，近10場射入8球，結果以14個入球結束首個效力修咸頓的球季，季後斯特羅克拒絕[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]的收購出價<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3811759.stm |title=Saints reject Phillips bid |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2004-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040617075548/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3811759.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但斯特羅克自己卻在8月23日被辭退<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3590316.stm |title=Sturrock leaves Saints |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2009-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091214061726/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/3590316.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2004年至2005年英格蘭超級聯賽|新球季]]展開，菲臘斯與修咸頓一直表現平平，直到2005年1月5日對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]才首次梅開二度，雙方3-3平手<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4130171.stm |title=Southampton 3-3 Fulham |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108180341/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4130171.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月15日1-2負於[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]的比賽完場前因攔截罰球而弄傷[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[韌帶|韌帶]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4150635.stm |title=Newcastle 2-1 Southampton |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530010106/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4150635.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，需養傷3周<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4183621.stm |title=Injury blow for striker Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530004116/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4183621.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月15日修咸頓最後一戰對[[曼聯|曼聯]]1-2敗北後篤定降級，結束27年在頂級聯賽的生涯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4525113.stm |title=Southampton 1-2 Man Utd |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2009-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427115404/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4525113.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，菲臘斯整季射入13球。

季後有傳言由史特根執教的[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]有意以70萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]收購菲臘斯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4080760.stm |title=Lowe denies Phillips Celtic talk |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530002441/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4080760.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但菲臘斯希望留在超級聯賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4089026.stm |title=Phillips considers Saints future |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530010143/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4089026.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終選擇投效阿士東維拉<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4634047.stm |title=Phillips set for £1m Villa switch |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530002849/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4634047.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===阿士東維拉===
2005年6月29日菲臘斯以100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉會費加盟阿士東維拉，簽約兩年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4635519.stm |title=Phillips completes Villa switch |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803183949/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4635519.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。穿著20號球衣，菲臘斯與[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]的[[胡安·巴勃罗·安赫尔|安祖]]及稍後加盟的[[米兰·巴罗什|-{zh-hk:巴路士;zh-hans:巴罗什}-]]在前線合作。2005年8月13日聯賽開鑼日，開賽僅4分鐘菲臘斯即首開紀錄，最終2-2賽和[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4126966.stm |title=Aston Villa 2-2 Bolton |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530002532/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4126966.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月中對[[托特纳姆足球俱乐部|熱刺]]賽前熱手觸傷小腿<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4714531.stm |title=Delaney completes Villa run-out |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530002842/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4714531.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，小休4場趕及在10月16日「伯明翰城打吡」復出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4308094.stm |title=Fit-again Phillips targets derby |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530004342/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4308094.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，射入唯一入球，作客[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]小勝1-0<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4322124.stm |title=Birmingham 0-1 Aston Villa |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2010-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100425151713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4322124.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但斷斷續續的膝蓋傷患使菲臘斯難於長期出任正選<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4520880.stm |title=Phillips undergoes ankle surgery |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2005-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051215134330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4520880.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，11月尾做手術從膝蓋取出一塊骨頭碎片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4573304.stm |title=Phillips rules out FA Cup return |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005116/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/4573304.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿士東維拉成績不佳（聯賽排第16位）及球員與球會主席對立，加上領隊{{tsl|en|David O'Leary|大卫·奥莱利}}（David O'Leary）離職<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/irish/5196872.stm |title=O'Leary parts company with Villa |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2009-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090116015448/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/irish/5196872.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由[[馬田·奧尼爾|馬田·奧尼爾]]接任，促使整季只有5個入球的菲臘斯下堂求去。

===西布朗===
當菲臘斯在[[2005年至2006年英格蘭超級聯賽|2005/06年]]下半球季在阿士東維拉鬱鬱不得志，即有傳聞他會回歸新近由舊拍檔昆尼（Niall Quinn）收購及帶領的新特蘭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/5235722.stm |title=Sunderland want old boy Phillips |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530003225/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/5235722.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新特蘭及西布朗同獲阿士東維拉首肯與菲臘斯商討條件，但最終菲臘斯選擇西布朗，於8月22日落實加盟，轉會費70萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約兩年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/5274054.stm |title=Phillips makes move to West Brom |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2006-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060907043445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/5274054.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，菲臘斯稍後透露他在近年已三度搬家，故這次決定留下來，加盟鄰近的西布朗。2006年10月14日菲臘斯連中三元，西布朗作客5-1擊敗[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/5415658.stm |title=Ipswich 1-5 West Brom |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530005951/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/5415658.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年2月17日在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第五圈作客對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]射入扳平2-2的一球是其個人第200個入球<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6349633.stm |title=Middlesbrough 2-2 West Brom |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2007-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070304212431/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6349633.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月6日在球季最後一日，西布朗7-0大勝[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]，菲臘斯造出本季第二次「大三元」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6602897.stm |title=West Brom 7-0 Barnsley |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2008-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080412222142/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6602897.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，整季射入19球，協助西布朗晉級季後升級附加賽。升級附加賽準決賽對同是來自黑鄉（Black Country）鄰近的死敵[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]，5月13日首回合作客憑菲臘斯梅開二度僅勝3-2<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6645893.stm |title=Wolves 2-3 West Brom |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2014-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427071411/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6645893.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，5月16日次回合主場菲臘斯一箭定江山，1-0小勝，兩回合累計4-2晉級[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊]]決賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6649727.stm |title=West Brom 1-0 Wolves |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516092231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6649727.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月28日決賽不幸0-1僅負於[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6689971.stm |title=Derby 1-0 West Brom |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2017-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801234400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6689971.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，未能重返[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|超級聯賽]]。 季後菲臘斯進行足踝小手術<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/6707725.stm |title=Phillips and Clement have surgery |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2007-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071007210556/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/6707725.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]展開，2007年9月30日主場5-1擊敗[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]，菲臘斯射入兩球<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7008072.stm |title=West Brom 5-1 QPR |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2007-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017162559/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7008072.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，領隊[[托尼·莫布雷|托尼·莫布雷]]（Tony Mowbray）認為兩名攻擊球員菲臘斯及[[伊斯美·米拿|伊斯美·米拿]]（Ishmael Miller）可互補不足<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7020797.stm |title=Mowbray pays tribute to strikers |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530003308/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7020797.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。菲臘斯獲選入「[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|冠軍聯賽]]每周陣容」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/staticFiles/9a/92/0,,10794~103066,00.pdf |title=Coca-Cola Championship Team Of The Week (01/10/2007) |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2007-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071129061901/http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/staticFiles/9a/92/0%2C%2C10794~103066%2C00.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

菲臘斯開季7場射入6球，銳不可當。10月初菲臘斯因膝傷缺陣兩場，初步檢驗沒有大問題而恢復操練<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7038020.stm |title=Phillips comeback boosts Baggies |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2007-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071018070327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7038020.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月6日主場對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]，下半場頭球建功後因膝傷需用擔架抬離場<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7076428.stm |title=West Brom 1-1 Sheff Wed |accessdate=2008-04-28 |archive-date=2007-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071109073611/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7076428.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。休戰6周直到12月15日主場對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]才復出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7139198.stm |title=Phillips set for Charlton return |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530003235/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7139198.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，下半場替補上場即獲一球進帳<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7134200.stm |title=West Brom 4-2 Charlton |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2007-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071216142545/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7134200.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。復出後4場射入5球，獲頒12月份「冠軍聯賽每月最佳球員」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7176525.stm |title=Phillips is handed December award |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2008-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115152802/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7176525.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年1月12日作客升級競爭對手[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]，開賽僅2分鐘便先開紀錄，再加一球助攻，3-1獲勝協助西布朗重返榜首<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7172827.stm |title=Hull 1-3 West Brom |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2008-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115134436/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7172827.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。菲臘斯再入選「冠軍聯賽每周陣容」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/staticFiles/c2/ce/0,,10794~118466,00.pdf |title=Coca-Cola Championship Team Of The Week (14/01/2008) |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2008-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228183051/http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/staticFiles/c2/ce/0%2C%2C10794~118466%2C00.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年3月3日「2008年足球聯賽頒獎禮」（Football League Awards）在[[倫敦|倫敦]]舉行，菲臘斯獲得球員最高榮譽的「冠軍聯賽年度最佳球員」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7267383.stm |title=Phillips wins Championship award |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2008-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080302041101/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7267383.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，托尼·莫布雷認為菲臘斯是『天生具有敏銳觸覺及視野的入球者』<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml?xml=/sport/2008/01/14/sfghul114.xml Ageless Kevin Phillips fuels Albion's rise]</ref>。3月13日主場1-1賽和[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]，菲臘斯首開紀錄的入球是其個人聯賽第200個入球<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7287966.stm |title=West Brom 1-1 Crystal Palace |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2008-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080315072645/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7287966.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季末西布朗與菲臘斯商談續約，菲臘斯要求兩年合約，但西布朗希望續簽一年死約加一年生約<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7342674.stm |title=Talks on Phillips deal 'ongoing' |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2008-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080415104636/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7342674.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，菲臘斯透露沒有離隊意圖，將在季後才能確定續約條件<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7363652.stm |title=Phillips denies contract rumours |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archive-date=2008-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430212946/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7363652.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。西布朗的球迷將在球季最後一戰作客[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]時穿著[[超级英雄|超级英雄]]服飾以表揚綽號「超級奇夫」（''Super Kev''）的菲臘斯對球隊的貢獻<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wba.premiumtv.co.uk/page/News/0,,10366~1296499,00.html |title=Fans gear up for 'Super' day |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2012-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503101155/http://www.wba.co.uk/page/News/0%2C%2C10366~1296499%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年5月4日，西布罗姆维奇在联赛最后一轮以2-0击败[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]，获得[[英格兰足球冠军联赛|英冠联赛]]冠军，将在2008/09赛季出现在[[英超|英超]]赛场上。而菲利普斯也以22球成为了球队的最佳射手，在联赛射手榜上则同[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]的[[詹姆斯·比蒂|比亞堤]]并列第2名。

===伯明翰城===
在西布朗兩年的合約結束後，菲臘斯希望再續約兩年，但因年齡問題，西布朗只能提供一份一年合約，如期間上陣或超過19場聯賽，可再續簽一年，菲臘斯拒絕接受。2008年7月9日轉投[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠聯]]的[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]，簽約兩年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7497349.stm |title=Phillips leaves Baggies for Blues |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530003219/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7497349.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2008/09年球季]]揭幕戰對[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:谢菲尔德联;zh-hant:錫菲聯}-]]，菲臘斯下半場後補上陣，在完場前受傷補時射入，協助伯明翰城1-0旗開得勝<ref>{{en}} [http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7540910.stm Birmingham 1-0 Sheff Utd] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7540910.stm |date=20080810030500 }}，2008年8月9日，[[BBC|BBC]] Sport，於2008年12月28日查閱</ref>。在接下來對[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]及[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]連續兩場比賽均取得入球。11月21日作客[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]，在半場落後1-2，菲臘斯後補入替梅開二度反勝3-2<ref>{{en}} [http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7727156.stm Swansea 2-3 Birmingham] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7727156.stm |date=20081122005704 }}，2008年11月21日，[[BBC|BBC]] Sport，於2008年12月28日查閱</ref>，而在菲臘斯取得入球的7場比賽，伯明翰城均獲勝而回<ref>{{en}} [http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7745425.stm Phillips admires Blues battlers] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7745425.stm |date=20150530003313 }}，2008年11月24日，[[BBC|BBC]] Sport，於2008年12月28日查閱</ref>。2009年2月中，已射入13球的菲臘斯在2-0擊敗[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]時觸傷[[腿後腱|腿後腱]]，需要缺陣三星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7896947.stm |title=Birmingham hit by Phillips injury |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-18 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221205818/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7896947.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在他養傷時，[[澳洲|澳洲]][[澳大利亞職業足球聯賽|A-League]]球隊[[珀斯光荣足球俱乐部|珀斯光輝]]透露有意邀請加盟<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7965881.stm |title=Birmingham angry at Phillips bid |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-26 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331154650/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7965881.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。傷愈復出的菲臘斯只在對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]時獲派上陣，其餘各場均只列後備，未能取得入球，菲臘斯對缺乏出場時間感到困惑<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8010861.stm |title=Phillips 'frustrated' by campaign |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-21 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090424065401/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8010861.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直到5月3日英冠聯賽煞科日，復任正選的菲臘斯在作客對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]時射入成2-0，是他本季第14個入球，使他成為伯明翰城本季的首席射手<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/club_stats/default.stm |title=Birmingham Club Stats:Top Scorers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date= |accessdate=2009-05-04 |archive-date=2009-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211121523/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/club_stats/default.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終伯明翰城2-1獲勝，獲得聯賽亞軍及最後一個自動升級[[英超|英超]]的席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8015130.stm |title=Birmingham clinch top-flight spot |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-03 |accessdate=2009-05-04 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113002043/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8015130.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，連續兩年為不同球隊取得升級資格。升班後年歲已高的菲臘斯在競爭劇烈的[[英超|英超]]只能擔任板凳球員，上陣24場中有20場後補入替，仍可取得重要入球，合共有4球斬獲，成為球隊的「後備殺手」。於2010年6月18日獲球隊續約一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8748428.stm |title=Striker Kevin Phillips extends Birmingham contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-06-18 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2011-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110531142113/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8748428.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年2月27日伯明翰城在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]於[[2011年英格蘭聯賽盃決賽|聯賽盃決賽]]迎戰[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，爆冷門以2-1獲勝，菲臘斯擔任沒有上陣的替補球員，取得個人首面盃賽冠軍獎牌<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/9405702.stm |title=Arsenal 1-2 Birmingham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-02-27 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2020-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108182845/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/9405702.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年5月27日於伯明翰城降班[[英冠|英冠]]後，菲臘斯成為6名遭放棄的球員之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13573178.stm |title=Relegated Birmingham confirm exit of six players |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-27 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2011-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124213648/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13573178.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===黑池===
2011年7月10日菲臘斯以[[自由球員|自由身]]轉投剛降班返回[[英冠|英冠]]的[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，已達37歲高齡獲提供一年合約，並可優先續約12個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14098319.stm |title=Kevin Phillips joins Blackpool on free transfer |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-10 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2011-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923114938/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14098319.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊==
雖然菲臘斯在球會級水平獲得成功，但在8次代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]出賽卻沒有取得入球，更未嘗踢足一場90分鐘的比賽。1999年4月28日菲臘斯首披英格蘭戰衣出戰[[匈牙利國家足球隊|匈牙利]]。菲臘斯獲[[凯文·基冈|奇雲·基瑾]]選入[[2000年歐洲國家盃|2000年歐洲國家盃]]的決賽周大軍<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/euro2000/teams/england/772145.stm |title=Keegan names Euro 2000 squad |accessdate=2008-04-26 |archive-date=2012-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204121733/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/euro2000/teams/england/772145.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在3場分組賽中只能屈居沒有上場的後備。菲臘斯最後一次代表英格蘭於2002年2月13日出戰[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]。

